Baccha ada Curran, 1941 : 278
. Type locality: Brazil, Santa Catarina, Nova Teutônia. Holotype male (AMNH). Hull, 1949 : 95 (citation), 112 (key), 135 (redescription), 195 (fig. 20, female abdomen), 217 (fig. 116, male abdomen); Fluke, 1956 : 235 (catalog citation);
